<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="101" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1451,1520,1653]" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,453,1520,1545]" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Distribution and habitat:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[452,692,1521,1545]" class="Liliopsida" family="Hydrocharitaceae" genus="Ottelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Alismatales" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="songmingensis">
<emphasis box="[452,692,1521,1545]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Ottelia songmingensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
presently is only recorded from Songming County, 
<collectingRegion box="[1260,1448,1521,1545]" country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Yunnan Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[136,203,1557,1581]" name="China" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">China</collectingCountry>
. It grows along streams, where the water depth is from 
<quantity box="[794,861,1557,1581]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" unit="cm" value="40.0">40 cm</quantity>
to 
<quantity box="[894,935,1557,1581]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" unit="m" value="1.0">1 m</quantity>
or deeper.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="101" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="0.[136,1451,1520,1653]" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,278,1593,1617]" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Note:—</emphasis>
This species is close to 
<taxonomicName box="[539,781,1593,1617]" class="Liliopsida" family="Hydrocharitaceae" genus="Ottelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Alismatales" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="guanyangensis">
<emphasis box="[539,781,1593,1617]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">Ottelia guanyangensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[836,1021,1593,1617]" class="Liliopsida" family="Hydrocharitaceae" genus="Ottelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Alismatales" pageId="0" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fengshanensis">
<emphasis box="[836,1021,1593,1617]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">O. fengshanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
but differs in owing unisexual flowers, long banded leaf and unwinged fruit.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
